show.description: Five years after a painful betrayal involving her child, she enters a flash marriage with a stranger—unaware he’s the CEO… and the child’s father. What begins as an escape from arranged marriages slowly blossoms into something real. A heart-tugging tale of hidden identities, rekindled love, and a family fate never saw coming.
